txt.en: Enter the Orc camp at Nuiharn
Anborn has asked you to defeat the Orcs and their leader Bloglok camped in the ruins of Nuiharn.\n\nNuiharn can be found in the hills to the north-west of Haerondir.

‘We've found an Orc camp not far from here, in the ruins of Nuiharn. They do not appear to be making a move toward the Camp of the Host, but it would be unwise to let them linger nearby. The last thing we need is to be ambushed on the road or flanked from the rear while we march to the Black Gate. We have learned that the Orc Captain Bloglok leads this camp. Head to Nuiharn and end this threat.'
‘Good to hear that Bloglok and his followers are no longer a threat to the Host of the West. Now we can focus on the road ahead.’
TBD\n\nYou should defeat Orcs in TBD Big Ruins.

Anborn has asked you to clear out the Orcs camped at Nuiharn.
